運動產業實務專題討論                    


  	This course is a study of the sports industry across all of its disciplines. The industry is studied in detail in many different aspects as it exists in society. Key aspects of the sports industry category, career opportunities, and future outlook are addressed. Specific topics will include major trends affecting the sports industry, career opportunities in the sports industry, and the sports industry in Taiwan.

課程教育目標 

E. 專業能力 
