課程概述 Course Description
       This course is a study of the sports industry across all of its disciplines. The industry is studied in detail in many different aspects as it exists in society. Key aspects of the sports industry category, career opportunities, and future outlook are addressed. Specific topics will include major trends affecting the sports industry, career opportunities in the sports industry, and the sports industry in Taiwan.This course is a study of the sports industry across all of its disciplines. The industry is studied in detail in many different aspects as it exists in society. Key aspects of the sports industry category, career opportunities, and future outlook are addressed. Specific topics will include major trends affecting the sports industry, career opportunities in the sports industry, and the sports industry in Taiwan.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
To critically evaluate major challenges confronting various segments To acquire an understanding of what careers you are qualified for or interested Specific topics will include major trends affecting the sports industry 

